[
  {
    "scene": "TitleScene",
    "file": "01-title.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "歡迎來到誰讓他煉器的！第二章，第一集，禍害成軍。"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "周墨在煉器峰的日子過得「精彩」——丹爐半夜唱歌、鍋爐接連爆炸、長老的頭髮越來越少。今天，他即將炸掉第三個鍋爐。但這一次，爆炸的範圍比預期大了一點。"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "scene": "ContentScene1",
    "file": "02-content1.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "新的實驗！這次我改良了壓力釋放模組。理論上，效率應該提高百分之三百。"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "三、二、一——啟動！"
      },
      {
        "character": "luyang",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "那個，不好意思打擾了，請問你們這裡有沒有投降表？"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "什麼？"
      },
      {
        "character": "luyang",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "我是問道宗新弟子陸陽，我的劍法叫「投降劍法」。剛才看到爆炸，想說先填好表，等一下可能用得上。"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "你的劍法叫投降劍法？"
      },
      {
        "character": "luyang",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "對啊！核心招式是「我認輸」和「別打了」。防守效率極高——因為對手通常笑到沒力氣繼續打。"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "從邏輯上來說，確實是最短路徑。你直接跳過了戰鬥過程，抵達了終點。"
      },
      {
        "character": "luyang",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "對吧！終於有人理解我了！其他人只會說我沒出息。"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "不不不，你是把「效率」做到了極致。這是一種高級演算法思維。"
      },
      {
        "character": "luyang",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "你，你是唯一一個說我好話的人。"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "scene": "ContentScene2",
    "file": "03-content2.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "mengjingzhou",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "等等，你們兩個在聊什麼？我從二十步外就感覺到了異常的邏輯波動。"
      },
      {
        "character": "luyang",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "這位是？"
      },
      {
        "character": "mengjingzhou",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "孟景舟，問道宗弟子。我的天賦是「單身光環」——方圓三丈內，所有女性都會自動遠離我。"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "這也是天賦？"
      },
      {
        "character": "mengjingzhou",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "宗門鑒定說是「被動技能，無法關閉」。連女修都繞著我走，所以我有很充足的時間做研究。"
      },
      {
        "character": "luyang",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "那你研究什麼？"
      },
      {
        "character": "mengjingzhou",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "為什麼我沒有女朋友。"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "你把單身當成一個研究課題？"
      },
      {
        "character": "mengjingzhou",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "二十三年了。我的論文已經寫到第七篇了，題目是「論問道宗女弟子的空間分布與我的絕緣性」。"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "我突然覺得，我們三個有一個共同點。"
      },
      {
        "character": "luyang",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "什麼？"
      },
      {
        "character": "mengjingzhou",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "什麼？"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "我們都不正常。"
      },
      {
        "character": "luyang",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "說得好有道理。"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "所以我提議，我們成立一個小組。叫「問道宗邏輯修正小組」。"
      },
      {
        "character": "mengjingzhou",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "邏輯修正？修正什麼？"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "修正整個修仙界對「正常」的定義。"
      },
      {
        "character": "luyang",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "我加入！不過我有一個條件——小組的第一條規則是「隨時可以投降」。"
      },
      {
        "character": "mengjingzhou",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "我也有條件——開會的時候不要提「女朋友」這三個字。"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "成交。順帶一提，我剛才忘了說——第三個鍋爐的爆炸範圍可能還沒結束。"
      },
      {
        "character": "luyang",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "我的投降表呢？"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "scene": "OutroScene",
    "file": "04-outro.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "感謝收看誰讓他煉器的！第二章第一集，禍害成軍。"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "問道宗邏輯修正小組正式成立。三個最不正常的弟子聚在一起，展開了全新的篇章。陸陽的投降劍法、孟景舟的單身研究、周墨的法寶實驗——問道宗從此再也沒有安寧的日子。"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "下集預告：三人組的第一個共同任務——探索後山的「低語洞窟」。聽說那裡住著一個上古大能的殘魂，但周墨覺得那只是一個「待修復的離線終端」。"
      }
    ]
  }
]
